### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Login admin démo
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@smartcampus.local",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### Me (remplacer TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP protégé — doit retourner 401 sans token
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/status

### ERP protégé — avec token admin
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/status
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP — semestre actif
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/semesters/active
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP — liste étudiants
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/students
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP — étudiant par téléphone (agent)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/students/by-phone/+243810000001
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP — notes + moyenne
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/students/1/grades
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Agent chat (phase 6)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+243810000001",
  "message": "Quelle est ma moyenne?"
}
